Involute Sans is a modern humanist sans-serif typeface designed to harmonize Bangla and Latin scripts within a single family. Crafted with precision and cultural sensitivity, it brings clarity, balance, and elegance to multilingual communication.

The design draws inspiration from natural geometric proportions, applying the Golden Ratio and Fibonacci sequence to achieve a refined sense of rhythm and harmony. Its letterforms are optimized for digital readability while maintaining sophistication for print media, ensuring a versatile user experience across contexts.
